{"tid":1517990,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬 連儂學校 搞大佢","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:42:29.000Z","uid":82068,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f962146ebb6d80532176ad60b0e7f321cb157078","tid":1517990,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幼稚園 小學 中學 大學<br />\n由校內到外 <br />\n行過就痴幾張 你吹得我漲<br />\n貼滿曬班狗d衰野"},{"pid":"9e5d586106569da2a5d0f9ecf727a375c200bb99","tid":1517990,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50ce3ad695d5acb71ea5ddaccecf9673c95700b","tid":1517990,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"壁報板？"},{"pid":"1dc852c176280bf71b63ee36f9327d474c16a357","tid":1517990,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b50ce3ad695d5acb71ea5ddaccecf9673c95700b","tid":1517990,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"壁報板？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"罷課依啲唔講啦<br />\n想講既係罷唔到課既小朋友可以做咩<br />\n<br />\n除左唔同啲犬二代玩，保障自己之外<br />\n你仲可以做好多野<br />\n<br />\n1.尋找志同道合既朋友仔<br />\n學生始終係中意埋堆玩，容易受人影響，可以weekend約埋去行下街，買下玩具，咁就唔怕單機啦，個圈仲可以日漸擴大，感染下啲唔敢出既人<br />\n<br />\n2.善用壁布<br />\n文宣咁靚，梗係趁班主任未到就釘哂上去<br />\n美化下課室<br />\n<br />\n3.乜都傾一餐<br />\n之前乜事都冇就傾下 kpop 傾下八卦 傾下動漫<br />\n但依家日日新鮮<br />\n一翻到去梗係同同學傾餐飽啦<br />\n琴日班狗有幾柒 佢地有幾賤<br />\n上線前應該有咩戰術(講梗打機)<br />\n買咩 gear  去邊課金(講梗打機)<br />\n小息講放學講轉堂講<br />\n課室操埸教員室門囗都係好地方<br />\n傾下計都比老師捉？咁個老師等比人篤灰啦<br />\n<br />\n4.尋找山區小孩/助養者<br />\n如果你好有需要/屋企人有助養開<br />\n不妨向身邊人求救/ 伸出援手<br />\n<br />\n不過睇到嘅學生可能得好少， 希望你哋喺學校都可以有個好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89869db629f606d543a8509eac685cb9cb6f4e28","tid":1517990,"uid":284480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f2507117d838c754abaeeb08b9a676d4e3fdb0","tid":1517990,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b50ce3ad695d5acb71ea5ddaccecf9673c95700b","tid":1517990,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"壁報板？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"唔係 係成間學校內外貼曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52012100668dde09cd46258c1f8dc71aaca980fc","tid":1517990,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8tMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=968d4b93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed22ce1bd0cff7a0238191057cbd171ecfe09ec8","tid":1517990,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"我果間傾好哂痴邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b0750d5747f0f5b8c8d85a25f059f4ea9055db","tid":1517990,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}